»CL4:SCENETIME/SHOWTIME by Darkage
»CL9:--------------------------------------
»CL1:Wade writes:»CL0: Amiga Inc etc don't need
to waste their money on advertising
when they have franchise mags like
this; overflowing with game adverts,
fat cat speeches and commercial
conference reports, in cahoots with
naive optimism. However, I'd be lying
if I said I disliked the magazine. The
charts and gallery sections manage to
compensate for the lacking features
and its regularity motivated the
entire scene. In terms of design, it
remained very traditional, yet was
always a pleasant environment in which
to read.
»CL9:--------------------------------------
