»CL4:OEPIR RISTI by Citron
»CL9:--------------------------------------
»CL1:Wade writes:

»CL0:Sufficient graphics and functional
code. The highlight of this mag was
always the title picture. The article
content, while spattered with the
occasional scene scoop was, on the
whole, very dull and banal. Oepir
Risti was impaired by numerous
factors: minimal support, annual
releases and an overall lack of heart.
It's death is not something I mourn.






»CL3:Sane writes:

»CL2:The best lifestyle magazine ever. It's
not a Scenemagazine as there were too
less Scene-related articles in it. The
design was superb. It was my favourite
mag of -both- Scene life and real
life!! I hope Henrik manages to
release it once again.

»CL9:--------------------------------------

