»CL4:INSOMNIA by Looker House
»CL9:--------------------------------------
»CL1:Wade writes:

»CL0:I have to give the magazine full
credit on its appearance. The graphics
are beautifully pixelled, with a very
unique and artistic style. The fonts
and layout are very reminiscent of
ROM, which is no bad thing; making it
readable and comfortable on the eye.
Article wise it contains everything
one can expect from a leading scene
mag, though its delays mean that their
subjects are somewhat outdated or
irrelevant at its time of release. 






»CL3:Sane writes:
»CL2:
I don't like the design. The articles
of the issues I have seen were average
and only Bytebreakers and Shade's work
were worth to be read.

»CL9:--------------------------------------

